♪ Touching the very part of me♪

34:03.869 --> 34:06.561
♪ It's making my soul sing♪

34:06.630 --> 34:09.426
♪ I'm crying out for more♪

34:09.495 --> 34:14.397
♪ Your love is king♪

34:14.466 --> 34:16.295
♪ I'm coming on...♪

34:17.434 --> 34:19.678
[glass clinking]

34:23.613 --> 34:25.097
[laughs]

34:25.166 --> 34:27.720
Um...

34:27.789 --> 34:29.619
I would love to take a moment

34:29.722 --> 34:32.587
to thank you all
for coming tonight,

34:32.656 --> 34:38.248
and also to thank Joe and --
and Lettie for inviting me

34:38.317 --> 34:43.426
to help celebrate my beautiful,
brilliant daughter, Carmen.

34:43.495 --> 34:45.117
[crowd "awws"]

34:45.186 --> 34:49.432
Darling, getting to know you
these past few weeks --

34:49.501 --> 34:51.813
it's been one of the greatest
gifts of my life.

34:51.917 --> 34:57.543
So, I have a little gift
for you!

34:57.647 --> 34:59.166
[chuckles] Come on up here.

34:59.269 --> 35:00.926
[chuckles]

35:03.480 --> 35:04.516
For you.

35:04.619 --> 35:05.586
[chuckles] What?

35:05.655 --> 35:08.106
Open it.

35:08.175 --> 35:09.935
WOMAN: Small box. [chuckles]

35:10.004 --> 35:12.317
Oh, my God. They're so nice.

35:12.386 --> 35:13.559
Oh, good. Good, good, good.

35:13.663 --> 35:16.735
Thank you. Thank you.

35:16.804 --> 35:19.738
-Ohh. [laughs]
-Ah!

35:19.807 --> 35:21.257
Well...

35:23.121 --> 35:26.607
Carmencita, I-I got you
something small,

35:26.676 --> 35:28.471
but with much love.

35:28.540 --> 35:29.989
Do you want me to open it?

35:30.093 --> 35:31.370
Only if you want.

35:39.033 --> 35:43.451
♪♪

35:43.520 --> 35:47.973
♪♪

35:48.042 --> 35:50.182
[sighs]

35:50.251 --> 35:53.323
Not everybody gets this,

35:53.392 --> 35:57.810
but, um, my art
means everything to me.

36:00.296 --> 36:04.369
I started holding a crayon
[chuckles] as soon as I could,

36:04.438 --> 36:05.956
and...

36:07.924 --> 36:10.651
But this was the first thing
I was ever proud of.

36:10.720 --> 36:13.067
[crowd "awws"]

36:14.379 --> 36:15.656
And you kept it.

36:15.725 --> 36:21.351
♪♪

36:21.420 --> 36:23.353
Thank you, Mami.

36:23.422 --> 36:27.254
[cheers and applause]

36:27.357 --> 36:29.532
[chuckles]

36:29.601 --> 36:31.706
I had a nice time tonight.

36:31.810 --> 36:34.399
I know. Me too.

36:34.468 --> 36:36.159
You ready to head out?

36:36.228 --> 36:39.852
Maybe just one more minute?

36:39.921 --> 36:44.167
[Tita's "Me Quedo Con Lo Bueno"
plays]

36:44.236 --> 36:46.687
♪ Me quedo con lo bueno♪

36:49.448 --> 36:52.520
♪ Me quedo con lo bueno♪

36:54.419 --> 36:57.836
♪ Me quedo con lo bueno♪

36:59.493 --> 37:02.461
♪ Me quedo con lo bueno♪

37:22.240 --> 37:23.413
-Gracias.
-Bien.

37:27.624 --> 37:28.625
Hmm?

37:28.694 --> 37:30.558
[speaking Spanish]

37:48.369 --> 37:50.958
♪ Red, red wine

37:51.061 --> 37:53.132
[vocalizing]

37:53.236 --> 37:55.894
[laughter]

37:55.963 --> 37:58.137
[speaks Spanish]

37:58.241 --> 37:59.760
Okay.

37:59.829 --> 38:02.072
[speaks Spanish]

38:05.317 --> 38:07.250
[wine pours]

38:38.868 --> 38:39.938
[sighs]

38:49.188 --> 38:50.811
To Los United States, huh?

38:52.606 --> 38:54.815
-To Los United States!
-United States.

38:54.884 --> 38:56.541
[laughs]

38:58.025 --> 39:01.304
[Lettie sighs, groans]

39:01.373 --> 39:06.792
You had a nice little dance
with Margaret.

39:06.896 --> 39:11.141
If you were trying to
make me jealous, it worked.

39:14.421 --> 39:15.836
Joe?

39:20.427 --> 39:21.669
Joe?

39:25.052 --> 39:26.502
I'm sorry.

39:29.436 --> 39:31.714
I'm sorry
I-I lied to you.

39:31.783 --> 39:34.613
I'm sorry I didn't tell you
Billy was back.

39:34.717 --> 39:37.444
I know you deserved better.

39:39.204 --> 39:40.757
But I need you.

39:40.826 --> 39:44.312
I-I need you to know
nothing happened between us.

39:44.416 --> 39:48.903
I-I know what you're thinking.
Nothing -- Nothing happened.

39:48.972 --> 39:51.043
What a relief -- you didn't
sleep with a priest.

39:51.112 --> 39:52.597
Thank you.

39:52.666 --> 39:54.495
Now how are we supposed to
get through this?

39:54.599 --> 39:56.359
You won't even
open up with me.

39:56.428 --> 40:00.121
"Open up" with you?
Is that what you want?

40:00.225 --> 40:04.402
You want me to
tell you how it felt

40:04.471 --> 40:06.611
to see you sneaking around
with my brother?

40:08.509 --> 40:11.719
It hurt.

40:13.790 --> 40:16.241
You lied to me, Lettie.

40:16.310 --> 40:20.452
For weeks.
And you want me to be open?

40:20.521 --> 40:23.731
You know how I feel about you,
how I always felt about you.

40:25.146 --> 40:29.806
Since the day we met,
you've come first in my life.

40:29.875 --> 40:31.981
Even when I was with Margaret,
I put you first.

40:32.084 --> 40:35.225
When my brother abandoned you,
I was there.

40:35.294 --> 40:36.848
Yo.
iNo mas yo!

40:38.608 --> 40:43.337
I gave...and I gave,

40:43.441 --> 40:44.683
and I gave!

40:46.478 --> 40:48.273
And this is what I get
in return?!

40:48.342 --> 40:51.621
-No, Joe, please.
-No, no, no, no, no.

40:51.690 --> 40:53.416
You wanted to hear it!

40:53.485 --> 40:54.935
[breathes shakily]

40:55.004 --> 40:57.800
Right? So hear it.

41:02.494 --> 41:03.495
I trusted you.

41:05.463 --> 41:09.536
Everything that
we have been through,

41:09.639 --> 41:11.848
from the day
that we came to this country.

41:11.917 --> 41:16.025
You put your faith in God,

41:16.128 --> 41:17.854
I put my faith in you.

41:19.131 --> 41:20.270
In us.

41:21.513 --> 41:25.344
And that trust was...

41:27.243 --> 41:30.108
It was the one thing
I could rely on.

41:30.177 --> 41:33.387
-Joe.
-You broke it.

41:33.491 --> 41:36.770
You broke it, and I don't think
we can get it back.

41:36.873 --> 41:37.978
LETTIE: Joe.

41:38.047 --> 41:45.744
♪♪

41:45.848 --> 41:47.159
[sighs]

41:47.228 --> 41:48.920
Joe.

41:50.300 --> 41:51.992
How's that for open?

41:52.061 --> 41:59.171
♪♪

41:59.240 --> 42:01.519
[breathes shakily]

42:05.695 --> 42:08.215
[knock on window]

42:11.114 --> 42:12.978
MARGARET: Forgive me, Father,
for I have sinned.

42:13.082 --> 42:18.156
I bribed a church official
to transfer a priest to Sonoma.

42:18.225 --> 42:23.541
♪♪

42:27.614 --> 42:34.344
♪♪

42:34.413 --> 42:41.110
♪♪

42:41.213 --> 42:47.944
♪♪

42:48.048 --> 42:54.882
♪♪

